WEBVTT	#Elemental Media Engine(TM) 2.18.0.0

00:00:00.383 --> 00:00:01.919
604

00:00:02.336 --> 00:00:05.297
[Shirose Yu
Ordinary Company Employee]

00:00:05.627 --> 00:00:06.631
Here it is

00:00:10.727 --> 00:00:11.678
Huh?

00:00:12.179 --> 00:00:15.516
Was the room
always this spacious?

00:00:26.276 --> 00:00:29.963
[Kuroda Koichi
President of Kuroda Group]

00:00:32.741 --> 00:00:33.992
Who are you?

00:00:36.674 --> 00:00:37.578
Oh?

00:00:41.083 --> 00:00:42.292
Get out now

00:00:47.839 --> 00:00:49.174
Wow

00:00:49.258 --> 00:00:50.581
Amazing

00:00:51.472 --> 00:00:52.894
What's with this face?

00:00:53.679 --> 00:00:54.513
Is it real?

00:00:54.930 --> 00:00:56.044
Let go of this

00:00:59.559 --> 00:01:01.208
Why?

00:01:15.326 --> 00:01:16.243
Is it your first time

00:01:17.996 --> 00:01:19.871
being touched by any chance?

00:01:24.388 --> 00:01:25.442
I got you

00:01:29.818 --> 00:01:30.851
Why

00:01:33.206 --> 00:01:34.081
Huh?

00:01:36.722 --> 00:01:38.342
Strange

00:01:38.426 --> 00:01:39.182
Usually

00:01:39.433 --> 00:01:40.939
I would have already
pushed away

00:01:42.477 --> 00:01:43.979
Does it look like my first?

00:01:46.440 --> 00:01:47.190
Huh?

00:01:51.278 --> 00:01:52.383
Wait a minute…

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:01.541
What?

00:02:03.104 --> 00:02:04.938
It's you who started it

